CR?"},{"pid":"5216c533218c0bedd92438450b5f0431268d60c4","tid":893293,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e3d019d7212aa7e4cfd17dd0da6fac63a0baa12","tid":893293,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T19:34:57.000Z","msg":"試下ACR?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"咩嚟？"},{"pid":"104afbd4bbdd0cf089ad73f830c8e8cc788ae1f7","tid":893293,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"我自己寫個APP 係咪都唔得?"},{"pid":"93208f4b3b24dccb7ba020b9ba73c74a81cde745","tid":893293,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5216c533218c0bedd92438450b5f0431268d60c4","tid":893293,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e3d019d7212aa7e4cfd17dd0da6fac63a0baa12","tid":893293,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T19:34:57.000Z","msg":"試下ACR?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"咩嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nll.acr&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nll.acr%26hl%3Den_US&d=oG1EFAUqW3bYmJBQjyEZZGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=81316c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nll.acr&amp;hl=en_US</a>"},{"pid":"926f02853bed8adb1519247e0a12f09e547b0478","tid":893293,"uid":69353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"root左用boldbeast<br />\n原生就得呢個方法"},{"pid":"1eedd4e99175f5c2a9147d60e9c6eb34a33f93a2","tid":893293,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T17:13:21.000Z","msg":"Android Pie makes it impossible to record calls with third-party apps<br />\n<a href=\"https://bgr.com/2018/08/15/android-pie-update-call-recording-apps-dead/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbgr.com%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2Fandroid-pie-update-call-recording-apps-dead%2F&d=oG1EFAUqW3bYmJBQjyEZZGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=12d3ed6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bgr.com/2018/08/15/android-pie-update-call-recording-apps-dead/</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We would like to inform our users that<span style=\"color: blue;\"> there will be no call recording workaround on Android 9 and above</span>,&rdquo; wrote the developers of the <span style=\"color: red;\">Call Recorder &ndash; ACR </span>app on their forums. &ldquo;<span style=\"color: blue;\">No call recording app will be able to do so</span>.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Boldbeast</span>, the developer of another app called Call Recorder, first told their users to attempt to use Record Mode 13 within the app after updating to Android 9.0, but when a forum member explained that it still didn&rsquo;t work, the developer said the following: &ldquo;<span style=\"color: blue;\">So root is the only way to go, [there] is no other solution in the market</span>.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThere were rumors that call recording would return in Android Pie, and there was even hard evidence that Google was at least looking into it on the Issue Tracker, but now that the update has launched, the feature is nowhere to be found. That doesn&rsquo;t mean it won&rsquo;t be added later down the road, but for now, the only way to record a call on Android is to root it, which, just in case you weren&rsquo;t aware, will void the warranty on your device."},{"pid":"2b1927c68ca7de12a8587bcdf20bb4aafa4968fc","tid":893293,"uid":72908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"咁8.1 呢？"},{"pid":"6b9cd2a92641e1fb956f03afd12c993394bca917","tid":893293,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93208f4b3b24dccb7ba020b9ba73c74a81cde745","tid":893293,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5216c533218c0bedd